<H2>Future Work</H2>
<UL>
<LI>Debuggers and run-time visualization tools.
<LI>Software tools for writing parallel/distributed programs.
<LI>Performance improvements for scientific applications.
<LI>Programming tools for data mining.
<LI>A distributed run-time kernel for PLinda.
<LI>Suggestions -- please feel free to send mail to <!WA16><A HREF="mailto:plinda@cs.nyu.edu">plinda@cs.nyu.edu</A>.
</UL>
